                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7668" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1922</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3570 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“绿”争上游:绿色创新如何赋能首钢园高质量发展？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Strive for excellence by going green: How can green innovation empower the high-quality development of Shougang Park?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙新波，李俊悦，刘剑桥，孙世鑫，苑丽秀，汤凯文，郭素云</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">首钢集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京首钢工业园区；绿色创新；绿色管理；可持续发展；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Beijing Shougang industrial park; Green innovation; Green management; Sustainable development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在可持续发展、双碳目标等绿色发展理念的影响下，人们的环保意识不断增强，高污染的传统老工业园区被迫停产，如何再激活老工业园区发展新动能成为亟待解决的难题。首钢园在集团领导的带领下积极探寻改造对策，发现绿色创新是首钢园激活工业遗存价值、应对可持续发展挑战和实现高质量发展的关键。首钢园攻关绿色技术、强化绿色服务、开展绿色管理，通过不断绿色创新打造绿色产业园区，形成具有首钢特色的商业模式，成为老工业园区绿色转型的典范。本案例围绕首钢园绿色创新实践，帮助学生掌握绿色创新的概念内涵、驱动因素、挑战与对策，并通过与德国鲁尔区比较，引导学生对首钢园绿色创新实践进行深入思考，为老工业园区通过绿色创新实现高质量发展提供有益借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the influence of sustainable development, double carbon target and other green development concepts, people’s awareness of environmental protection has been increasing. Highly polluting traditional old industrial parks are forced to stop production, and how to reactivate the old industrial parks to develop new momentum has become an urgent problem. Shougang Park, under the leadership of the Group, actively explored transformation countermeasures and found that green innovation is the key to activate the value of industrial heritage, meet the challenges of sustainable development and achieve high-quality development. Shougang Park taps into green technology, strengthens green services, carries out green management, creates a green industrial park through continuous green innovation, forms a business model with Shougang characteristics, and becomes a model for green transformation of old industrial parks. This case focuses on the green innovation practice of Shougang Park, helping students grasp the conceptual content, drivers, challenges and countermeasures of green innovation. Through comparison with the Ruhr region of Germany, it guides students to think deeply about the green innovation practices of Shougang Park, and provides useful reference for the old industrial park to achieve high-quality development through green innovation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色创新；绿色管理；可持续发展；商业模式创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
